rComments: Took 2 classes with him. You need to pay attention to the class material and his examples explained in class. Papers grades were little bit low but within my expectation. I tried to book several office hour with him and it helped a lot with my assignment and finals.

Stay away from this professor if you can. Super long and boring lectures and lots of readings. He is a tough grader and will give low grades arbitrarily (I am typically in the mid 80s range in other media studies classes, but I got 50s and 60s with him). Talking to him during office hours helps a little bit, but my grades still suffered.
teacherRatingTags: ['Tough grader', 'Lots of homework', 'Get ready to read']
